### Auth
POST http://localhost:8087/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "doctor@example.com", "password": "dev123456" }

### Templates list
GET http://localhost:8087/api/templates

### Create template
POST http://localhost:8087/api/templates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Receita Simples",
  "description": "Modelo básico",
  "fields": [
    {"key":"patientName","label":"Paciente","type":"text"},
    {"key":"drug","label":"Medicamento","type":"text"}
  ]
}

### Documents list
GET http://localhost:8087/api/documents

### Create document
POST http://localhost:8087/api/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateId": "TEMPLATE_ID",
  "title": "Receita de teste",
  "content": { "patientName":"João", "drug":"Dipirona 500mg" }
}

### Sign document
POST http://localhost:8087/api/documents/DOC_ID/sign

### PDF
GET http://localhost:8087/api/documents/DOC_ID/pdf